General.Name: FG Merger Corp.
General.Description: FG Merger Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus its search for a target business in the financial services industry in North America. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Itasca, Illinois. FG Merger Corp. operates as a subsidiary of FG Merger Investors LLC.
